snippet.title: Neural Shock - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Neural Shock on Steam Now - Released June 19th 2024:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2862970/Neural_Shock/

In Neural Shock, you must must cleanse the world of horrid and bloodthirsty creatures by utilizing turrets, traps, wits and weapons. Choose from various class choices with unique play styles and over 30 different turrets and traps.

Neural Shock is a PC and mobile Tower Defense / Action RPG game released in June 2024 on Windows, MacOS and Linux. Also targeting to release on Android and iOS later in 2024.
